Consider the following algorithm, where A[1..n] is an array of numbers:

func(A[1..n]):
    for i = 1 to n-1:
        for j = n to i+1:
            if (A[j] < A[j-1]):
                swap(A[j], A[j-1])
        ### Loop Invariant ###
    return A

Consider the following partially specified invariant. Fill in the missing blanks to form an invariant that is correct and helps prove the correctness of the algorithm.

Loop Invariant: elements in A[ Blank 1 ... Blank 2 ] are Blank 3 .
